Package: NGLVieweR
Title: Interact with protein databank files with the NGL.js JavaScript Library
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c( 
    person("Niels", "van der Velden", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "n.s.j.vandervelden@gmail.com"),
    person("Alexander", "Rose", role = "cph", comment = 'NGL.js library'))
Description: Provides an 'htmlwidgets' interface to 'NGL.js'.
    NGLvieweR can be used to visualize and interact with protein databank files in R and Shiny applications.
    It includes a set of API functions to manipulate the viewer after creation in Shiny.
